# 🚀 NasCoder

**AI Assistant powered by AWS Bedrock with Claude models**

NasCoder is a powerful command-line AI assistant that brings the capabilities of Claude AI models directly to your terminal through AWS Bedrock.

```
███╗   ██╗ █████╗ ███████╗ ██████╗ ██████╗ ██████╗ ███████╗██████╗ 
████╗  ██║██╔══██╗██╔════╝██╔════╝██╔═══██╗██╔══██╗██╔════╝██╔══██╗
